S = (A + B)^2
D = 10 \cdot A + B.\;\;\;\;
|S - D| = 27 \iff  |(A + B)^2 - (10A + B)| = 27, \quad (0 < A < 10, \;0 \le B < 10)
\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\iff (A+B)^2 - (10A + B) = 27,\quad\text{OR}\quad (10 A + B) - (A + B)^2 = 27
\text{with}\quad(0 < A < 10, \;0 \le B < 10)
